{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775866454279,"sessionID":"ses_2861e289bffeEA9L147U2ruOXd","part":{"id":"prt_d79e3a0e3001FpbN7TM0qVdlrr","messageID":"msg_d79e390dc0011TuiN4plaqkGCZ","sessionID":"ses_2861e289bffeEA9L147U2ruOXd","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-3788b269d70f43bc827b36f0a4f224bb","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/cmd/cli/design.md","limit":50},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/cmd/cli/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # CLI Build Command Design\n2: \n3: **AR**: AR-021 — CLI build 命令  \n4: **Module**: cmd/cli  \n5: **Language**: Python  \n6: **Size**: M\n7: \n8: ## Overview\n9: \n10: The `build` command is a core component of the AgentCube CLI that builds container images from packaged agent workspaces. It supports both local Docker builds and cloud-based builds, with automatic version management and comprehensive error handling.\n11: \n12: ## Architecture\n13: \n14: ### Component Diagram\n15: \n16: ```\n17: ┌─────────────┐\n18: │   CLI (Typer)   │\n19: │  main.py     │\n20: └──────┬──────┘\n21:        │ build()\n22:        ▼\n23: ┌─────────────────────┐\n24: │  BuildRuntime       │\n25: │  build_runtime.py   │\n26: └──────┬──────────────┘\n27:        │\n28:        ├──► MetadataService\n29:        │    └── load_metadata()\n30:        │    └── save_metadata()\n31:        │\n32:        └──► DockerService\n33:             └── check_docker_available()\n34:             └── build_image()\n35:             └── get_image_info()\n36: ```\n37: \n38: ### Key Components\n39: \n40: 1. **CLI Layer** (`agentcube/cli/main.py`)\n41:    - Typer command definition\n42:    - User input validation\n43:    - Error handling and user feedback\n44: \n45: 2. **Runtime Layer** (`agentcube/runtime/build_runtime.py`)\n46:    - Build orchestration\n47:    - Version management\n48:    - Build mode selection\n49: \n50: 3. **Service Layer**\n\n(Showing lines 1-50 of 624. Use offset=51 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# CLI Build Command Design\n\n**AR**: AR-021 — CLI build 命令  \n**Module**: cmd/cli  \n**Language**: Python  \n**Size**: M\n\n## Overview\n\nThe `build` command is a core component of the AgentCube CLI that builds container images from packaged agent workspaces. It supports both local Docker builds and cloud-based builds, with automatic version management and comprehensive error handling.\n\n## Architecture\n\n### Component Diagram\n\n```\n┌─────────────┐\n│   CLI (Typer)   │\n│  main.py     │\n└──────┬──────┘","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/cmd/cli/design.md","time":{"start":1775866454262,"end":1775866454277}}}}
